---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="JG Concrete Pumping | Dallas–East Texas"
  description="Owner-operated 38-meter boom pump serving the Dallas–East Texas Corridor. Residential, commercial, and civil concrete pumping. Call Jacob at (469) 704-4227."
>

  <!-- ==============================
       HERO
  ============================== -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container hero-inner">
      <span class="section-label">Dallas–East Texas Corridor</span>
      <h1>Concrete Pumping.<br/>Done Right.</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">
        38-meter boom pump. Owner-operated by Jacob Gordon on every single job.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-primary">Get a Free Quote</a>
        <a href="tel:+14697044227" class="btn btn-outline">Call (469) 704-4227</a>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-stats">
        <div class="stat">
          <strong>38m</strong>
          <span>Boom Reach</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-divider"></div>
        <div class="stat">
          <strong>DFW + East Texas</strong>
          <span>Service Area</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-divider"></div>
        <div class="stat">
          <strong>Owner-Operated</strong>
          <span>Every Job</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- ==============================
       SERVICES
  ============================== -->
  <section id="services" class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-label">What We Do</span>
        <h2>Concrete Pumping for Every Job</h2>
        <p>One 38-meter boom pump handles residential, commercial, and civil pours across the Dallas–East Texas Corridor.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="services-grid">
        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 12l8.954-8.955a1.126 1.126 0 011.591 0L21.75 12M4.5 9.75v10.125c0 .621.504 1.125 1.125 1.125H9.75v-4.875c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125V21h4.125c.621 0 1.125-.504 1.125-1.125V9.75M8.25 21h8.25"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Residential</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>House slabs, footings & driveways</li>
            <li>Townhouse & duplex pours</li>
            <li>Multi-unit residential</li>
            <li>Pool Decks</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3.75 21h16.5M4.5 3h15M5.25 3v18m13.5-18v18M9 6.75h1.5m-1.5 3h1.5m-1.5 3h1.5m3-6H15m-1.5 3H15m-1.5 3H15M9 21v-3.375c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h3.75c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125V21"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Commercial & Industrial</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Tilt-panel construction</li>
            <li>Warehouse & factory floors</li>
            <li>Data centres & industrial sites</li>
            <li>Commercial developments</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M11.42 15.17L17.25 21A2.652 2.652 0 0021 17.25l-5.877-5.877M11.42 15.17l2.496-3.03c.317-.384.74-.626 1.208-.766M11.42 15.17l-4.655 5.653a2.548 2.548 0 11-3.586-3.586l6.837-5.63m5.108-.233c.55-.164 1.163-.188 1.743-.14a4.5 4.5 0 004.486-6.336l-3.276 3.277a3.004 3.004 0 01-2.25-2.25l3.276-3.276a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.336 4.486c.091 1.076-.071 2.264-.904 2.95l-.102.085m-1.745 1.437L5.909 7.5H4.5L2.25 3.75l1.5-1.5L7.5 4.5v1.409l4.26 4.26m-1.745 1.437l1.745-1.437m6.615 8.206L15.75 15.75M4.867 19.125h.008v.008h-.008v-.008z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Civil & Structural</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Retaining walls & pits</li>
            <li>Culverts & civil infrastructure</li>
            <li>Structural pours</li>
            <li>Retention structures</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ==============================
       ABOUT
  ============================== -->
  <section id="about" class="section section--alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-label">About</span>
        <h2>Meet Jacob Gordon</h2>
        <p>Concrete Industry Management professional with field experience across operations, quality control, and materials — backed by a dedicated industry degree.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="about-grid">
        <div class="about-main">
          <div class="about-headshot-row">
            <img src="/JG-Concrete-Pumping/jacob.jpg" alt="Jacob Gordon" class="headshot" />
            <div class="headshot-info">
              <h3>Jacob Gordon</h3>
              <p>Owner & Operator<br/>BS Concrete Industry Management<br/>Rockwall, TX</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p>
            Jacob Gordon is a concrete industry professional with hands-on experience across
            every level of the supply chain — from aggregate sourcing and batch plant operations
            to quality control and field testing. That depth of knowledge is what separates
            JG Concrete Pumping from operators who simply drive a truck.
          </p>
          <p>
            Jacob holds a <strong>BS in Concrete Industry Management from Texas State University</strong> —
            one of the most specialised concrete credentials available in the United States. He has worked
            directly with two of the industry's largest companies, Heidelberg Materials and Centex Materials,
            in operational and quality control roles across Texas. He currently serves as a
            Lab Instructor at Texas State, training the next generation of concrete professionals
            for ACI Field Grade I certification.
          </p>
          <p>
            When you hire JG Concrete Pumping, you're not just getting a pump and an operator.
            You're getting someone who understands your mix, your placement requirements, and what
            it takes to get the pour right the first time.
          </p>

        </div>

        <div class="about-credentials">
          <div class="edu-card">
            <div class="edu-card-header">
              <div class="edu-badge">TSU</div>
              <div>
                <strong>Texas State University</strong>
                <span>San Marcos, TX</span>
              </div>
              <span class="edu-dates">Completed 2026</span>
            </div>
            <div class="edu-degree">BS Concrete Industry Management</div>
            <p>One of the only dedicated concrete degrees in the United States — a rigorous program covering mix design, materials science, quality control, and construction operations.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="why-matters">
            <h4>Professional Credentials</h4>
            <div class="wm-points">
              <div class="wm-point">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5"/></svg>
                BS Concrete Industry Management — Texas State University
              </div>
              <div class="wm-point">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5"/></svg>
                ACI Field Grade I — certified concrete testing professional
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ==============================
       SAFETY & CERTIFICATIONS
  ============================== -->
  <section class="section safety-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-label">Safety &amp; Certifications</span>
        <h2>Safety Is Not an Afterthought</h2>
        <p>Every job site carries risk. Jacob holds industry certifications that go well beyond the minimum — because the crews working around the pump deserve nothing less.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="cert-grid">
        <div class="cert-card">
          <div class="cert-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="cert-body">
            <div class="cert-badge">OSHA 30</div>
            <h3>Construction Safety &amp; Health</h3>
            <p>OSHA's 30-hour construction course is the standard for site supervisors and safety leads. Covers fall protection, electrical hazards, struck-by incidents, excavation, and more.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="cert-card">
          <div class="cert-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="cert-body">
            <div class="cert-badge">MSHA 10</div>
            <h3>Mine Safety &amp; Health</h3>
            <p>MSHA certification demonstrates competency in the hazard recognition standards required at quarry and aggregate operations — expanding the job sites we can safely service.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="cert-card">
          <div class="cert-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/><path d="M8 21h8M12 17v4"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="cert-body">
            <div class="cert-badge">ACI Grade I</div>
            <h3>Field Testing Technician</h3>
            <p>American Concrete Institute Field Grade I certification — qualified to perform slump, air content, unit weight, and cylinder casting tests to verify mix quality on the pour.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ==============================
       SERVICE AREA
  ============================== -->
  <section id="service-area" class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-label">Where We Work</span>
        <h2>Dallas–East Texas Corridor</h2>
        <p>Covering the DFW Metroplex and East Texas via the I-20 corridor — one of the strongest construction territories in the US.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="area-grid">
        <div class="area-card">
          <div class="area-card-header">
            <h3>Dallas–Fort Worth Metroplex</h3>
            <span class="area-badge">Primary Market</span>
          </div>
          <p>The core of our territory. DFW is ranked <strong>#2 in the US</strong> for new home builder permit volume and <strong>#1 nationally</strong> for industrial permits — with a booming pipeline of data centres, warehouse construction, and commercial development.</p>
          <div class="area-tags">
            {['Dallas', 'Fort Worth', 'Rockwall', 'Mesquite', 'Garland', 'Arlington', 'Plano', 'Frisco', 'McKinney', 'Irving', 'Grand Prairie', 'Richardson', 'Allen', 'Denton', 'Lewisville', 'Carrollton'].map(city => (
              <span class="area-tag">{city}</span>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="area-card">
          <div class="area-card-header">
            <h3>East Texas</h3>
            <span class="area-badge area-badge--secondary">Secondary Market</span>
          </div>
          <p>Reliable boom pump service throughout East Texas. Whether you're building in Tyler, Longview, or anywhere along the I-20 corridor, JG Concrete Pumping brings the same professionalism and direct owner service as every DFW job.</p>
          <div class="area-tags">
            {['Tyler', 'Longview', 'Lindale', 'Whitehouse', 'Bullard', 'Flint', 'Mineola', 'Canton', 'Terrell', 'Forney', 'Kaufman'].map(city => (
              <span class="area-tag">{city}</span>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="market-stats">
        <div class="mkt-stat">
          <div class="mkt-stat-value">$50.33B</div>
          <div class="mkt-stat-label">Texas Construction Spending — Leads the Nation</div>
        </div>
        <div class="mkt-stat">
          <div class="mkt-stat-value">#2</div>
          <div class="mkt-stat-label">DFW New Home Permit Volume, Nationally</div>
        </div>
        <div class="mkt-stat">
          <div class="mkt-stat-value">#1</div>
          <div class="mkt-stat-label">DFW Industrial Permits — ~1/3 of TX commercial sq ft</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ==============================
       CONTACT
  ============================== -->
  <section id="contact" class="section section--alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-label">Get in Touch</span>
        <h2>Request a Quote</h2>
        <p>Call or fill in the form below. You'll hear back from Jacob directly.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="contact-layout">
        <div class="contact-info">
          <div class="contact-method">
            <div class="contact-method-icon">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="22" height="22" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 6.75c0 8.284 6.716 15 15 15h2.25a2.25 2.25 0 002.25-2.25v-1.372c0-.516-.351-.966-.852-1.091l-4.423-1.106c-.44-.11-.902.055-1.173.417l-.97 1.293c-.282.376-.769.542-1.21.38a12.035 12.035 0 01-7.143-7.143c-.162-.441.004-.928.38-1.21l1.293-.97c.363-.271.527-.734.417-1.173L6.963 3.102a1.125 1.125 0 00-1.091-.852H4.5A2.25 2.25 0 002.25 4.5v2.25z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <strong>Phone / Text</strong>
              <a href="tel:+14697044227">(469) 704-4227</a>
              <span>Fastest way to book — call or text Jacob directly</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="contact-method">
            <div class="contact-method-icon">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="22" height="22" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M21.75 6.75v10.5a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.25 2.25h-15a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.25-2.25V6.75m19.5 0A2.25 2.25 0 0019.5 4.5h-15a2.25 2.25 0 00-2.25 2.25m19.5 0v.243a2.25 2.25 0 01-1.07 1.916l-7.5 4.615a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.36 0L3.32 8.91a2.25 2.25 0 01-1.07-1.916V6.75"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <strong>Email</strong>
              <a href="mailto:Jacob@gordonconcrete.com">Jacob@gordonconcrete.com</a>
              <span>For quotes and project details</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="contact-method">
            <div class="contact-method-icon">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="22" height="22" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 10.5a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"/><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19.5 10.5c0 7.142-7.5 11.25-7.5 11.25S4.5 17.642 4.5 10.5a7.5 7.5 0 1115 0z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <strong>Based in</strong>
              <span>Rockwall, TX</span>
              <span>Serving Dallas–Fort Worth & East Texas</span>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>

        <form class="quote-form" method="POST" action="https://formspree.io/f/xnjornlv">
          <div class="form-row">
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="name">Your Name *</label>
              <input type="text" id="name" name="name" placeholder="John Smith" required />
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="phone">Phone Number *</label>
              <input type="tel" id="phone" name="phone" placeholder="(XXX) XXX-XXXX" required />
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="email">Email Address</label>
            <input type="email" id="email" name="email" placeholder="your@email.com" />
          </div>
          <div class="form-row">
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="site-address">Site Address / Suburb *</label>
              <input type="text" id="site-address" name="site_address" placeholder="Dallas, TX" required />
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="pour-date">Preferred Pour Date *</label>
              <input type="date" id="pour-date" name="pour_date" required />
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="form-row">
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="pour-type">Type of Pour *</label>
              <select id="pour-type" name="pour_type" required>
                <option value="" disabled selected>Select type...</option>
                <option>Residential Slab / Footing</option>
                <option>Driveway / Path</option>
                <option>Townhouse / Duplex / Multi-Unit</option>
                <option>Commercial / Industrial Floor</option>
                <option>Tilt-Panel Construction</option>
                <option>Pool Surround</option>
                <option>Retaining Wall</option>
                <option>Civil / Structural</option>
                <option>Other</option>
              </select>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="pour-volume">Estimated Volume (yd³)</label>
              <input type="number" id="pour-volume" name="pour_volume" placeholder="e.g. 30" min="1" />
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="message">Additional Details</label>
            <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="3" placeholder="Site access notes, concrete supplier, any other details..."></textarea>
          </div>
          <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-submit">Send Quote Request</button>
          <p class="form-note">We respond within a few hours. For urgent jobs, call directly.</p>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  /* ==============================
     HERO
  ============================== */
  .hero {
    background: var(--color-primary);
    color: #fff;
    padding: 7rem 1.5rem 6rem;
  }

  .hero-inner { max-width: 820px; }

  .hero h1 {
    color: #fff;
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 5.5rem);
    font-weight: 900;
    line-height: 1.05;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin: 0.75rem 0 1.5rem;
  }

  .hero h1 br { display: block; }

  .hero-sub {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    max-width: 480px;
  }

  .hero-actions { display: flex; gap: 1rem; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-bottom: 2.5rem; }

  .hero-stats { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1.5rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }

  .stat { display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
  .stat strong { font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--color-accent); line-height: 1; }
  .stat span { font-size: 0.78rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); margin-top: 0.2rem; }
  .stat-divider { width: 1px; height: 36px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); }


  /* ==============================
     SERVICES
  ============================== */
  .services-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .service-card {
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: 2rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .service-icon {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .service-card h3 {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .service-card ul {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.4rem;
  }

  .service-card li {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.4rem;
  }

  .service-card li::before { content: '—'; color: var(--color-accent); flex-shrink: 0; }

  /* ==============================
     ABOUT
  ============================== */
  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .about-headshot-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .headshot {
    width: 90px;
    height: 90px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center top;
    border: 3px solid var(--color-accent);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .headshot-info h3 {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
  }

  .headshot-info p {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .about-main p { color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 0.97rem; }

  .why-matters {
    background: var(--color-bg);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--color-accent);
  }

  .why-matters h4 { color: var(--color-primary); margin-bottom: 0.75rem; font-size: 0.95rem; }

  .wm-points { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem; }

  .wm-point {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .wm-point svg { color: var(--color-accent); flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px; }

  /* Edu card */
  .edu-card {
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .edu-card-header {
    background: var(--color-primary);
    padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .edu-badge {
    background: var(--color-accent);
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .edu-card-header strong { display: block; color: #fff; font-size: 0.95rem; }
  .edu-card-header span { display: block; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65); font-size: 0.8rem; }

  .edu-dates {
    margin-left: auto;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 600;
